[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      5[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The Python companion is a well-structured, pedagogically excellent implementation of nurse staffing optimization using Google OR-Tools' CP-SAT solver. The code correctly formulates the constraint satisfaction problem with binary decision variables, implements both hard and soft constraints, handles infeasible scenarios gracefully, and demonstrates real-time call-off handling. DynamoDB code properly uses Decimal conversion. The logical flow builds understanding progressively from problem assembly through solving to storage. Comments are generous and explain the "why" effectively.
