[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     68[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     69[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   Additionally, PTO blocks further reduce capacity: RN-003 loses 3 days (up to 3 shifts) and RN-006 loses 4 days (up to 4 shifts), making the gap even wider.
